        <p>
          What was MMBase taglib?
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access to MMBase data
<pre>
<![CDATA[
   <mm:cloud>
     <mm:listnodes type="news">
         <h1><mm:field name="title" /></h1>
     </mm:listnodes>
   </mm:cloud>
]]>
</pre>
          </li>        
